Package game

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Card
    Card is a class representation of a standard poker card It is defined by it's value (2-A) and its suit (1-4)
    Combo
    Combo is a class that finds and holds the best combo among a 7 card hand
    Deck
    Deck is a class representation of a standard poker deck.
    Game
    Game is our class representation of our poker game It holds all our poker components and handles rounds
    Player
    Player is a class representation for a poker player The class player composes of its hand and the amount of money they have
